---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Medical disclaimer" description="The educational boundary for BES3 content.">
  <section class="page-hero shell">
    <div><p class="eyebrow">SAFETY NOTE</p><h1>Information is not diagnosis.</h1></div><p
      class="lede"
    >
      BES3 explains cosmetic skincare. It does not diagnose, treat or replace care from a qualified
      professional.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="section reading-width article-body">
    <h2>Use good judgment</h2><p>
      Patch test new products where appropriate, follow the product label and stop use if a product
      causes a concerning reaction. Seek professional advice for persistent, painful, rapidly
      changing or worrying symptoms.
    </p>
    <h2>Product information changes</h2><p>
      Formulas, directions, regulations and availability can change by market. Confirm current
      information with the official manufacturer or a qualified clinician before acting on it.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
